  • Classes in com.github.codeteapot.jmibeans used by com.github.codeteapot.jmibeans 
    Class and Description
    Machine
    Machine available in the platform context.
    MachineBuilder
    Responsible for registering facets during the creation of a machine.
    MachineBuilderContext
    Context in which a machine is created.
    MachineBuildingException
    Exception that is thrown during the machine build process if an error occurs.
    MachineCatalog
    Catalog of machine profiles used by a platform adapter.
    MachineFacetFactory
    Factory used when registering machine facets.
    MachineFacetInstantiationException
    Exception thrown when an error occurs during instantiation of a machine facet.
    MachineProfile
    Characteristics of a set of machines from the catalog.
    MachineRealm
    Set of recognized users of a machine.
    MachineSessionPool
    Properties of the session pool created to establish sessions on a machine.
    PlatformContext
    Access to the context generated by the platform adapter.
    PlatformEventSource
    Source through which events produced by the platform adapter are fired.
